data.description: Charming and Modern 4-Bedroom Family Home with Mother-in-Law Suite    Discover this beautifully customized 4-bedroom home, featuring a convenient 2-car garage and a cozy mother-in-law suite with a full bath and walk-in closet. Key highlights include:    * Smart Home Features: Smart thermostat, keyless front door entry, and energy-efficient double pane windows.  * Stylish Interiors: Luxury vinyl flooring, 9ft ceilings, and natural light throughout.  * Outdoor Appeal: Extended back patio, mature trees, and a well-maintained lawn with Saint Augustine grass.  * Efficient Kitchen: Gas stove, built-in cabinets, island, and elegant white cabinetry. Fridge negotiable.  * Comfortable Living Room: Spacious open-concept design.  * Primary Suite: Walk-in shower with seat, dual vanities, and granite countertops.  * Community Perks: Access to a new pool, park, and active HOA.  This home combines comfort with modern amenities, making it an ideal choice for a relaxed and convenient lifestyle. ***Pool is being completely remodeled and is expected to open in the Summer.
